<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 03:15:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国防部长称台湾不寻求与中国开战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-is-not-seeking-war-with-china-defence-minister-says-2024-06-17/</link><description>台湾国防部长顾维钧周一表示，台湾并不寻求与北京开战，其政策是建立防御性、多层次的威慑能力，使中国更难占领该岛。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 03:11:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-is-not-seeking-war-with-china-defence-minister-says-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国5月工业产出不及预期，零售销售成亮点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-may-industrial-output-misses-forecasts-retail-sales-bright-spot-2024-06-17/</link><description>中国5月份工业产出落后于预期，房地产行业依然疲弱，这给北京方面增加了政策支持以提振经济增长的压力，但由于假期的推动，零售销售超出了预期。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 02:24:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-may-industrial-output-misses-forecasts-retail-sales-bright-spot-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国新房价格跌幅创近10年来最快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-new-home-prices-fall-fastest-clip-nearly-10-years-2024-06-17/</link><description>官方数据周一显示，5月份中国新房价格跌幅为逾9-1/2年来最快，尽管政府努力遏制供应过剩并支持负债累累的开发商，但房地产行业仍难以触底。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 02:05:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-new-home-prices-fall-fastest-clip-nearly-10-years-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>1-5月中国房地产投资下滑加剧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-property-investment-slump-worsens-january-may-2024-06-17/</link><description>尽管政策制定者加倍努力支持陷入困境的行业和提振消费者信心，但中国的房地产投资在 1 月至 4 月下降 9.8% 后，2024 年前 5 个月仍同比下降 10.1%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 02:04:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-property-investment-slump-worsens-january-may-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行维持关键政策利率不变符合预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-leaves-key-policy-rate-unchanged-expected-2024-06-17/</link><description>周一，中国央行在到期中期贷款展期时，如预期维持关键政策利率不变，并从银行体系抽走部分资金。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 01:28:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-leaves-key-policy-rate-unchanged-expected-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>美元坚挺，欧元低迷；人民币无视中国数据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-euro-wallows-near-recent-lows-market-braces-china-data-2024-06-17/</link><description>由于对欧洲政治前景的持续担忧，欧元徘徊在一个多月低点附近，美元周一坚挺。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 01:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-euro-wallows-near-recent-lows-market-braces-china-data-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国数据公布前，美国消费者需求疲软，油价小幅下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-inch-down-weaker-us-consumer-demand-ahead-china-data-2024-06-17/</link><description>周五的调查显示美国消费者需求疲软，且交易员等待全球最大原油进口国中国公布关键经济数据，周一亚洲早盘油价下跌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 00:59:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-inch-down-weaker-us-consumer-demand-ahead-china-data-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因中国数据喜忧参半、欧元承压而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-17/</link><description>亚洲股市周一大多走软，因喜忧参半的中国经济消息凸显了该国的坎坷复苏，而欧洲的政治不确定性削弱了风险偏好，并使欧元处于守势。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 00:43:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警：菲律宾补给船在仁爱礁与中国船只发生碰撞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-says-philippine-supply-ship-illegally-intruded-waters-second-2024-06-16/</link><description>中国海警周一表示，一艘菲律宾补给船在非法侵入南海仁爱礁附近海域后，与一艘中国船只危险接近，导致轻微碰撞。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 23:33:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-says-philippine-supply-ship-illegally-intruded-waters-second-2024-06-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国投资者热衷海外资产刺激财富流入香港</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-offshore-assets-spurs-hong-kong-wealth-inflows-2024-06-16/</link><description>自中国放宽“财富通”计划的投资规则以来，这一趋势一直在加速。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 23:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-offshore-assets-spurs-hong-kong-wealth-inflows-2024-06-16/</guid></item><item><title>由于成本、签证障碍，中国出境游复苏滞后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-outbound-travel-recovery-lags-due-costs-visa-snags-2024-06-16/</link><description>复苏的延迟正在打击与旅游相关的公司、酒店和零售商。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 23:02:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-outbound-travel-recovery-lags-due-costs-visa-snags-2024-06-16/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：为中国数据洪流做好准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-16/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 21:48:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-16/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚阿尔巴尼斯与中国李克强举行“坦诚”会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-albanese-chinas-li-discuss-trade-jailed-writer-2024-06-16/</link><description>澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞和中国总理李强周一会面，这是中国总理七年来首次访问该国，东道主的议程包括贸易关系、地区安全和一名被监禁的澳大利亚作家。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 14:06:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-albanese-chinas-li-discuss-trade-jailed-writer-2024-06-16/</guid></item><item><title>支持者称中国总理访华前澳大利亚作家的判决维持不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-writers-sentence-upheld-ahead-china-premiers-visit-say-supporters-2024-06-16/</link><description>周日，澳大利亚作家杨恒均的支持者表示，北京高级人民法院维持了对他的死刑缓期执行，并在中国总理李强抵达澳大利亚两周前向澳大利亚官员转达了这一决定。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 12:43:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-writers-sentence-upheld-ahead-china-premiers-visit-say-supporters-2024-06-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国武汉天宇表示，被列入美国制裁名单可能会影响外汇交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-wuhan-tianyu-says-inclusion-us-sanctions-list-may-impact-forex-2024-06-16/</link><description>中国武汉天宇信息产业有限公司周日表示，美国将其列入制裁名单是“单方面”行为，可能会影响这家数据安全公司的外汇结算。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 10:09:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-wuhan-tianyu-says-inclusion-us-sanctions-list-may-impact-forex-2024-06-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>